{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"731e203de0","title":"对陈云来信的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"06085d2a3f","index":0,"year":1972,"month":7,"day":22,"articleId":"731e203de0"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"a2f6c6af57","name":"陈云","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji51","name":"毛泽东全集第51卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/51-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji51":{"comments":[{"id":"e502d37962","publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"731e203de0","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈云，原任中共中央副主席、国务院副总理。“文化大革命”中，被解除了中共中央委员之外的领导职务。1972年7月21日，他给毛泽东并中央写信，反映他在江西南昌下放的情况，请求中央根据他的身体情况，给他分配力所能及的工作。信中写道：“如果没有适当的工作可分配，可否参加北京老同志学习班？参加学习班之后，可否在我身体还能走动的几年在春秋季节仍到外地下面去着着？如果可以这样办的话，因为我不能坐飞机，可否破例在往返的路上给一个能烧暖气的公务车，避免受冷感冒，也可延长一点在外地走动的时间。”本篇一写在陈云的这封信上：本篇二写在这封信的信封上"},{"id":"67d7fbf741","publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"731e203de0","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"总理，指周恩来。"}],"contents":[{"id":"5a9ba3285a","type":"title","text":"对陈云来信的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"731e203de0"},{"id":"e502d37962","type":"paragraph","text":"印发。请中央商定。我看都可以同意。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"731e203de0"},{"id":"67d7fbf741","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"731e203de0"},{"id":"afbaf82473","type":"paragraph","text":"七二年七月二十二日请总理办。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"731e203de0"}],"page":{"id":"fbaf6ca9dd","publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"731e203de0","start":327,"end":327}}}},"__N_SSG":true}